<section class="section" aria-labelledby="home-intro">
    <p class="section-kicker">Start here</p>
    <h2 id="home-intro" class="section-title">Getting started with speedrunning</h2>

    <p class="section-lead">
        A source of truth for the setup side of speedrunning, explained game-by-game.
    </p>

